Megatron can't hear you, he's in a comm-jamming zone, Switchblade, 
however, has hacked the comps and fixed his commlink so that it can 
send and recieve. =)

--- Switchblade ---

Switchblade hears the commlink, and smiles. "Why hello, Ragnus, you 
are speaking to Switchblade. Megatron is in commlink jamming zone, 
and can't hear you. We are currently engaged in battle, come to these 
coordinates, NOW. Switchblade out." He ends the commlink and looks 
back on the battle. His two inch spider heads towards Torca.
